data.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

1. Male or female, \>30 years of age of any race;
2. A Body Mass Index between 18.5 and 29.9 kg/m2 (inclusive);
3. Clinical diagnosis according to the Brain Bank diagnostic criteria of idiopathic Parkinson's Disease (2 of 3 cardinal symptoms - bradykinesia, rigidity, tremor -mus

Inclusion Criteria:

Age between 18 and 80 years;

Diagnosed with Parkinson's Disease based on the MDS criteria, confirmed by a movement disorder neurologist;

Modified Hoehn and Yahr stage between 1 and 2.5;

No prior use of entacapone;

MMSE score ≥ 26;

BDI (Beck Depression Inventory) score \< 15
